9
00:02:15,916 --> 00:02:17,750
- ( chuckles )

10
00:02:25,916 --> 00:02:27,041
- HMM?

11
00:02:30,916 --> 00:02:33,166
- MM, SUCH SPIRIT.

12
00:02:43,916 --> 00:02:45,041
- ( chuckles )

13
00:02:57,875 --> 00:03:00,625
- BUT YOUR TIME HAS
NOT COME QUITE YET.

14
00:03:00,708 --> 00:03:04,000
- JUST KILL HER.
WHY NOT BE DONE WITH IT NOW?

15
00:03:04,083 --> 00:03:07,083
- BECAUSE THERE IS STILL
ONE MORE.

16
00:03:07,166 --> 00:03:08,666
- CLEVER.

17
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:11,291
SO YOU'RE GOING TO USE ONE
AS BAIT FOR THE OTHER.

18
00:03:11,375 --> 00:03:12,750
- ( gasps )

19
00:03:12,833 --> 00:03:15,125
- Chu: NO WONDER THEY CALL
YOU THE COLD-BLOODED KILLER.

20
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:16,666
- ( chuckles )

21
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,833
- ( metal clangs )

22
