- ( clicks )

25
00:03:39,708 --> 00:03:41,166
- ( blade snicks )
- ( yells )

26
00:03:56,583 --> 00:03:59,291
- IT SEEMS I'M JUST IN TIME

27
00:03:59,375 --> 00:04:00,708
TO HELP YOU.

28
00:04:12,708 --> 00:04:15,791
- IF YOU'RE REALLY HERE
TO HELP ME,

29
00:04:15,875 --> 00:04:17,791
I'D LIKE TO KNOW WHY FIRST?

30
00:04:18,916 --> 00:04:20,375
- THIS MOMENT...

31
00:04:22,083 --> 00:04:24,125
